Engage in dramatic mech warfare to protect mankind from invading monsters.
Fast, gorgeous fights with great controls. This is one of our favourite action games.
Combats furieux et explosifs pour ce jeu d’action incontournable.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Booming with anime-style action, Implosion feels like it was forged in some techno-marvel future. Spectacular visuals and spellbinding music bolster an epic tale that pits you—one of Earth’s few survivors—against the monsters who stole our homeworld. Fighting in your War-Mech battle suit’s a blast, with legions of ghastly foes ready for your lethal sword and fearsome firepower. If you like games long on style and ambition, this one’s for you.
